OL,3,C'Humbled': Surgeon instrumental in the
OL,4,Crecovery of Southport victims honoured
OL,6,FA surgeon who played a vital role in
OL,7,Ftreating children injured in the
OL,8,FSouthport knife attack has been named
OL,9,Fin the King's Birthday Honours.
OL,11,FVittoria Bucknall, a consultant trauma
OL,12,Fand orthopaedic surgeon at Alder Hey
OL,13,FChildren's NHS Foundation Trust, has
OL,14,Fbeen awarded the British Empire Medal
OL,15,F(BEM) for services to children and
OL,16,Fyoung people.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
