OL,3,C'Humbled': Surgeon instrumental in the
OL,4,Crecovery of Southport victims honoured
OL,6,FHer work is said to have been crucial
OL,7,Fto the survival of several children
OL,8,Ffollowing the Southport attack in July
OL,9,F2024, which unfolded during a Taylor
OL,10,FSwift-themed dance workshop, claimed
OL,11,Fthe lives of Alice da Silva Aguiar,
OL,12,Fnine, Elsie Dot Stancombe, seven, and
OL,13,FBebe King, six.
OL,15,FEight more children and two adults
OL,16,Fwere injured, including the seven-year-
OL,17,Fold daughter of the person who
OL,18,Fnominated her for the honour.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
