OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781348571
OL,3,C'Humbled': Surgeon instrumental in the
OL,4,Crecovery of Southport victims honoured
OL,6,FThe surgeon's expertise was credited
OL,7,Fas key to the survival of several
OL,8,Fchildren caught up in the incident. Ms
OL,9,FBucknall said she was "humbled" after
OL,10,Fbeing recognised for her work.
OL,12,FOne of the injured children, the
OL,13,Fnominator's daughter, was airlifted to
OL,14,FAlder Hey with more than 30 stab
OL,15,Fwounds and a life-threatening bleed.
OL,17,FShe required swift stabilisation and
OL,18,Ftwo marathon six-hour surgeries led by
OL,19,FVittoria and her team.
OL,26,@qD@WOUqD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
