PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781348571
OL,3,C'Humbled': Surgeon instrumental in the
OL,4,Crecovery of Southport victims honoured
OL,6,FThanks to Ms Bucknall's skill and
OL,7,Fcommitment, the young girl made an
OL,8,Fextraordinary recovery, regaining use
OL,9,Fof her arms and fingers, and returning
OL,10,Fto cartwheeling, dancing, drawing, and
OL,11,Fwriting.
OL,13,FSpeaking about the honour, Ms
OL,14,FBucknall, who lives in Edinburgh,
OL,15,Fsaid: "I'm absolutely humbled and
OL,16,Foverwhelmed to be receiving the medal.
OL,18,F"It is a little surreal and I am very,
OL,19,Fvery honoured."
OL,26,@wD@GOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
