CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781348571
OL,3,C'Humbled': Surgeon instrumental in the
OL,4,Crecovery of Southport victims honoured
OL,6,FThe nominator described the response
OL,7,Ffrom her and her colleagues as "above
OL,8,Fand beyond," adding that the team
OL,9,Ffaced challenges more akin to a
OL,10,F"combat situation" than routine
OL,11,Fmedical care.
OL,13,FMs Bucknall's support did not end with
OL,14,Fsurgery, she continued to visit the
OL,15,Fchild in intensive care and as an
OL,16,Foutpatient, offering ongoing
OL,17,Freassurance to the family.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@LO]rD@AOUrD@RO]
