OL,3,C'Humbled': Surgeon instrumental in the
OL,4,Crecovery of Southport victims honoured
OL,6,FThe British Empire Medal recognises
OL,7,Fnot only her surgical skill but the
OL,8,Fextraordinary compassion and
OL,9,Fdedication shown in the aftermath of
OL,10,Fthe tragedy.
OL,12,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,13,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,14,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,15,Four region.
